proj78.xml.parser
Interface XmlParseEventListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
XmlDocumentBuilder
public interface XmlParseEventListener

Allows for implementing classes to register themselves with an XML parser and be notified of the significant parse events that are generated by it.

Author:
K.A., copyright (c) 2008
